BLO - blue variation of darkair theme for gnome-shell 
Now gnome-shell 3.4-3.6-3.8 -3.9.3 - compatible
Please notify me about any error you should find
Get the latest version always on gnome-look.org
launchpad & ppa is just going to be installed
.deb and rpm packages to come


Version 3.9.3 - published 27.06.2013 (published version: 3)
gnome-shell 3.4-3.6-3.8 -3.9.3 compatible (tested with ubuntu saucy and ppa/ricotz
- includes all the latest 3.4 fixes 
- fixed notification overlay problem 
- minor fixes, overlay notification fix

GNOME DAILY BUILD / PPA-RICOTZ (so 3.9.3-user) - PLEASE READ
Actually in gnome-shell is a bug (see bugzilla.gnome.org - BUG 702801) , that mixes gdm and gnome-shell theme

To get the theme error-free, please use it also for gdm
To change gdm theme , please use gdm3setup

You will find a version for quite any distribution on 
https://github.com/Nano77/gdm3setup

