Version 3.9.1 - published 25.05.2013 
Version 1 -but numbered after highest tested compatible gnome-shell theme 
Blue variation of Darkair theme 


Installation

a) Copy Blue to /usr/share/themes (as superuser) or in your local .themes folder
b) Copy the .conky and the .lua folder to your home folder (both folders are inside the conky folder)
c) Copy the .conkyrc file to your home folder
d) for the weatherforecast version
    rename .conkyrccomplete in .conkyrc
    sudo dpkg -i conkyforecast.deb
    sudo apt-get -f install (fixes dependencies)
e) read the Readme for conky-forecast

If you do not wish to install the weatherforecast, please change in .configrc bg2.png to bg1.png 
